->

  Create Ad -> Upload Ad

    MP3 Video Input -> Firebase Queue -> NodeServer -> IPFS Upload
    -> Save IPFS HASH in UserTable -> Send Hash to DOM -> ANGULAR updates VIDEO tag, for preview Approval
     - User defines impression feedback, via multipul choice questions/basic question/links/description of product/website/links
     - User Selects Tags and User Data for targeted Ad Selection -> Inpressions have a price based on complexity, age, income
     - User approves the price per impression - Review Screen -> Submit

  Active Ad -> User Selects Ad
    -> Views each completed Impression with full data/feedback
    -> Options to cancle Ad, Pause Ad, Review and contest legitiemnt user feedback
